Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.69,0:00:02.76,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Success! Integrity!\NEvidence and its impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.76,0:00:04.80,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An endless drive\Nto become the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:05.85,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Somebody wants to\Ninterview the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.67,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But while we're anticipating\Nthe public's attention...{世間の注目期待していたら}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:09.23,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An unexpected case arises!{思わぬ事件に大発展！}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:10.78,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single\Ntruth for what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:12.54,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And looks like a kid,\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:14.30,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(0,250)}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry I kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for coming at a time when you're so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's no trouble at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you can see\Nhere on my card...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Kobayashi Sumiko,\Nthe homeroom teacher of class 1-B.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a freelance writer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...\NYes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd made a name for myself lately with my articles in women's magazines...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it seems I may have\Nbeen making too much of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! No, I just don't\Nread magazines very often...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not the least bit upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you\Nwant to see me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're here for a story\Nabout bullying or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know that my class\Ndoesn't have any problems like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no...\NNothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:13.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to do a story on...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "Detective Boys"\Nwho are in your class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-The Detective Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean that club Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nand his friends formed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:23.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I heard a lot about\Nthose children's activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they just randomly decided to\Ncall themselves the "Detective Boys"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In reality, they simply\Nlook for lost cats and so on...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:40.16,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey...\NMinami! Megumi! Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:42.04,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Haven't we heard those\Nnames somewhere before...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:45.04,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It says they're three fierce ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But members of\Nthe police told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That they also contribute their\Nservices with murder cases and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Particularly a boy by the\Nname of Edogawa Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the title of\Nthis article will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:04.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The 21st Century Revival\Nof the Boy Detectives Club!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm absolutely certain that\Nwill grab everyone's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Interview with the\NDetective Boys, Part I!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With us, the Detective Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, a writer named Sugimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} visited me after school yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told me he really wants to write a\Nhuman interest story about your activities...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And asked me to\Ncooperate with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have a cold,\NKobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's certainly not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though it doesn't seem\Nlike I have a fever yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:01.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I have a runny nose\Nand can't stop sneezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay,\NKobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you take any medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By any chance, do your eyes itch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was up late last\Nnight grading tests...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So my eyes must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:16.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's hay fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:18.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been strong against that kind of thing ever since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hay fever is\Ncaused when antigens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the substances that cause allergies, enter one's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Antibodies are created to fight off those antigens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And once those have accumulated\Ninside the body beyond a certain level...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The antigens and the\Nantibodies react to each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And get converted into substances that cause allergy symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But because the antigen-carrying pollen is limited to being formed only one time a year...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It takes many months and\Nyears for them to build up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, even if\Nthey were fine as a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:06:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are often cases of people\Ndeveloping hay fever in their 20's and 30's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?\NWhat about the interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We, the Detective Boys,\Nhave obviously gotta do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Looks like a\Nrain shower's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But those guys sure are late...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're{\i0} the ones who said we'd\Nmeet up 30 minutes beforehand, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.24,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:26.45,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}30 minutes before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.50,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We're gonna meet\Nup {\i1}30 minutes{\i0} before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:29.54,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You got that, Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.88,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What, you're asking {\i1}me{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah, I got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:36.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:39.09,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But are {\i1}you{\i0} okay\Nwith that, Kojima{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:39.84,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:42.18,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:43.72,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:46.06,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Dress normally\Ntomorrow, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:49.18,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes, because we want to have him see\Nthe Detective Boys just as we really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:51.40,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You sure are smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:52.90,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(0,500)}Yeah, let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're sorry\Nwe kept you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!\NWere you waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!\NYou guys are late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What've you been doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that was 'cause\NAyumi was taking forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I wanted\Nto do a bunch of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, she {\i1}is{\i0} a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let this slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, I guess\NI've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way,\Nwhere's Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When did she...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with those clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't what\Nwe talked about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:39.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, we {\i1}are {\i0}\Ngetting interviewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Mitsuhiko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We must not let ourselves be interviewed in anything but our very best attire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because so many\Npeople will be looking at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:07:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw...\NWhy did this have to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:02.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It starts raining right when\Nwe're going to be interviewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,God's so mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was sunny\Nall day yesterday, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko, this is your fault\Nfor telling us to dress normally!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:15.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that you, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My formal clothes are getting drenched in this rain, making them a complete mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My shoes are soaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And my parents just\Nbought them for me last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:31.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}These guys are\Ngetting {\i1}way{\i0} too into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as we have him let us use his\Ndryer or something before the interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it at the writer's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But TVs nowadays all\Ndisplay in high definition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we're filmed going into the home\Nwith wet spots from the rain on our clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's gonna be\NTV cameras coming, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:57.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, brother. Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're gonna\Ndo a special about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'm sure a beautiful\Nfemale TV reporter will be there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I hope it's\NMizunashi Rena{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She couldn't possibly come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, she's currently\Nlying in a hospital bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:20.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That anchorwoman who's part of the men in black...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently hasn't\Nregained consciousness yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This interview couldn't be\Nrelated to {\i1}them{\i0}, could it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how you think about it, inviting five kids to your house is bound to attract attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to picture them doing something that could leave a trail to them if someone saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't they operate in the shadows, where no one will sense them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, if they were planning to target either of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't have called\Non an adult to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:55.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I keep you all waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:03.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She looks just\Nlike Detective Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:05.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You forgot your glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to wear\Ncontacts for a change!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I look funny like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't look funny at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your clothes are feminine,\Nand look really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look even\Nprettier than normal, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks!\NI'm happy you think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This writer was a\Nreal looker, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it'd be better to\Ngive up on the contacts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Your eyes are itchy from your hay fever, so\Nbeing irritated by the contacts isn't good for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My glasses...\NI'll be fine if I wear my glasses, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:51.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, doing that's\Nmuch better for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like there isn't much pollen in\Nthe air right now because it started raining...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there could be a lot of pollen\Naccumulated in the writer's home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I think you should dust off that fancy\Ntrim really well before entering the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you don't bring\Nany pollen inside, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right. I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Miss?\NWas the writer handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, he\Nwasn't bad-looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's friendly and\Nvery easy to talk to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I'm sure you'll be able to get along with him pretty quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he said he's famous for his experience in writing for women's magazines...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I'm sure he knows\Nhow to handle children, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he's famous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he must live in an\Nunbelievably huge mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll have his own chef... and even a pastry chef, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:48.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must be gonna treat us to an awesome feast for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I {\i1}know {\i0}he will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's expecting\Na bit too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure looks that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't a mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this just\Na regular apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With this, don't\Nexpect a TV camera crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or a beautiful\Nfemale TV reporter, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now you all can talk more freely, without feeling nervous, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did that writer really say he\Nwanted to interview us in his home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These look to have no more than\Nsingle, nine square-meter rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the interview will\Nbe at a nearby restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to call him when we got to the bus stop down the street!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to call him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since we're already here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can get this over with more quickly if we have him interview us in his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he'll be surprised\Nwhen we all suddenly show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:12:59.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't make too\Nmuch noise in there, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is he out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the morning paper is still stuck in the mail slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So maybe he's still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's unlocked...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sugimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay out of the room, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you, who's acquainted with him, had a\Nstrand of your hair happen to fall in this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it only\Ncast suspicion on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For now, please call for an\Nambulance and the police, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because they might think it's a prank if we called, 'cause we're kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there's no\Nneed for an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His body's completely stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been dead\Nfor at least half a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Stiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dead for half a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:06.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And this could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}A-All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is\NSugimori Masato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, age 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a\Nfreelance writer, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had an appointment to meet with him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he wanted\Nto interview the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is how you found him when you got here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:34.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, when did he\Napproach you about that interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in the early evening the day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He stopped by the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means he was\Nalive until at least then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you tell Sugimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nthat we accepted the interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called Sugimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} before\Nnoon yesterday and told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the exact time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, just a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I called him from this\Nphone between third and fourth period...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I might know if\NI check the call log!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was 11:22 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that the murder took place after that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:23.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This camera tripod seems\Nto be the murder weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer made it this far into\Nthe room before bludgeoning him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means there's a strong chance\Nthat they were someone he knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the victim was a writer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could consider someone he interviewed as the perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's also possible it was someone who held a grudge against him for a scandalous article.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, but if he wrote an article about a celebrity or such...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might be a fan who\Nresented him over what he wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the suspects are countless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think there are four\Npeople who are suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:54.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? Take a look at the button for\Nthe answering machine on this phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:15:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-The light's blinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems to have\Nfour new messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, why do you think\Nthese four messages are suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look closer!\NAt the edge of that button!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood on it\Nhas been rubbed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!\NYou're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody pushed the answering machine button after the blood spattered on it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder who did\Nsomething like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:37.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was after the\Nvictim was attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the victim pushed it while barely\Nremaining conscious after the murderer fled...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would have called 110 for help,\Ninstead of checking the answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no blood\Non the victim's fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means that the\Nmurderer pushed the button?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:59.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can only think that the murderer turned the answering machine on after striking the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case,\Nwhy'd they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that was because they didn't want\Nthe deceased Sugimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to be discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way,\Neven if someone called...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would make them think he was out, so they wouldn't drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the key to this\Nroom is on the table...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the door was unlocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? The key...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think they would lock the door if they\Ndidn't want Sugimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to be found dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:35.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the remaining possibility is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:41.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Left a message on\Nthe answering machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To create an alibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That explains why they\Ndidn't bother to lock the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the discovery of\Nthe body was delayed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the estimated time of death became uncertain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:57.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't the alibi\Nthey made go to waste?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:58.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:01.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!\NLet's listen to these right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:03.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:09.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who {\i1}is {\i0} this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's hear the\Nvoices of the four suspects!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!\NW-Wait a minute, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we listen while recording it, just in case?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, we can listen to them\Nagain as many times as we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if we accidentally\Ndelete them while listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would cause a\Nlot of problems, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I ask the forensics team\Nto bring recording equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the killer's voice really\Non that answering machine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood that splattered on the machine's "on" button was partially smeared off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the murderer bludgeoned Sugimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They intentionally turned it on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And left a message on the\Nanswering machine to create an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:19:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But couldn't the murderer have done that on purpose in order to throw off the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, take a look\Nat that over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's blood on\Nthe front doorknob.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's proof that the\Nmurderer left in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without noticing there\Nwas blood on his or her fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There certainly is blood on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way the blood is smeared on the\Nanswering machine button wasn't intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like they had a\Nsudden bright idea to try to trick us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since there are no\Nfingerprints on the bloody doorknob...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It does look like the\Nmurderer was wearing gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going a little\Ntoo fast from the get-go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is fine for Detective Takagi and Inspector Megure, because they're used to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this is the first time Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} has seen your deductive reasoning skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she's belittled!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold yourself back a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean,\N"hold myself back?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:02.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's looking at me, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:03.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?\NAren't you always doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NDoing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your "Oh, hey!" or\Nyour "Isn't that funny?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put on your somewhat\Nabsent-minded child act.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:19.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if the public learns about your detective work...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:27.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They'll{\i0} eventually\Nget wind of it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:29.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I wasn't planning\Non talking much at this interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:35.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm not so sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Sugimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the victim, really a famous writer...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told me so himself\Nwhen he visited the school the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he'd made\Nquite a name for himself lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, isn't it strange that he's\Nnot living somewhere better than this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's always the chance that\NSugimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was lying through his teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! He...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, I know...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:12.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's kind of embarrassing,\Nnow that she's mentioned it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey!\NLook at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a funny key hanging from Sugimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s waist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See!\NIt's got a silver horsie on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he liked animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the key to a Ferrari.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The super-car?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Is that a super-car?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugimori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} may have been a man\Nwho spent everything he had on his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Sometimes, people will make huge cuts\Nto their living expenses to maintain a luxury car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the fact that he kept the keys to this room on a different chain...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:21:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Means he was\Nprobably showing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Oh, hey! Look at that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.68,0:22:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that kind of behavior that\Nmakes adults look down on us kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's cute, but you might\Nbe acting a bit {\i1}too{\i0} childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop\Ndoing things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:20.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}O-Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.08,0:22:24.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.46,0:22:30.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No matter how\NI go about doing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:35.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(0,500)}It's not gonna be easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.89,0:24:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...\NYour voice, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.80,0:24:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.76,0:24:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So our teacher\Nmight be the killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.85,0:24:09.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.56,0:24:12.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's only one person\Nwho has a solid alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.56,0:24:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, slow down...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.27,0:24:15.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.44,0:24:17.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-sensei{\r\be10}\Nwas suspicious of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.98,0:24:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hay fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.94,0:24:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, weren't all\Nthree of them involved with hay fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.49,0:24:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's\Nsomething I want to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.82,0:24:27.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Here it comes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.87,0:24:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan:\NInterview with the Detective Boys, Part II!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.87,0:24:36.33,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.87,0:24:36.33,Signs,,0,0,0,,Conan's
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.87,0:24:36.33,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.33,0:24:38.04,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(250,250)}Railroad crossing sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.71,0:24:40.38,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The movie's finally opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.38,0:24:41.76,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The Private Eyes' Éclair!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.76,0:24:43.01,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's 'Requiem'!
